msgid "The null hypothesis specifies that the first digits (1 - 9) in the data set are distributed according to %1$s."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis null menetukan bahwa angka pertama (1 - 9) dalam rangkaian data "
"didistribusikan menurut %1$s."

msgid "The null hypothesis specifies that the first two digits (10 - 99) in the data set are distributed according to %1$s."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis null menetukan bahwa dua angka pertama (10 - 99) dalam rangkaian "
"data didistribusikan menurut %1$s."

msgid "The null hypothesis specifies that the last digits (1 - 9) in the data set are distributed according to %1$s."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis null menetukan bahwa angka akhir (1 - 9) dalam rangkaian data "
"didistribusikan menurut %1$s."

msgid "The Bayes factor is computed using a Dirichlet(%1$s,...,%2$s%3$s) prior with %2$s = %4$s."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes dihitung menggunakan priori Dirichlet(%1$s,...,%2$s%3$s) dengan "
"%2$s = %4$s."

msgid "<b>Warning.</b> The <i>p</i>-value may be unreliable due to some expected counts being lower than 5."
msgstr ""
"<b>Peringatan.</b> Nilai-<i>p</i> mungkin tidak dapat diandalkan karena "
"beberapa penghitungan terharapkan lebih rendah dari 5."

