msgstr "Tingkat Positif Benar"

msgid "The null hypothesis specifies that the true positive rate of an unprivileged group is equal to that of the privileged (P) group."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis null menentukan bahwa tingkat positif benar dari grup tidak berhak "
