msgid "<u>Audit Risk Model</u>"
msgstr "<u>Model Risiko Audit</u>"

msgid "The Audit Risk Model is a method to reduce the required information from the sample on the basis of earlier assessments of inherent risk, control risk and analytical risk, while maintaining the desired audit risk.\n\nPrior to the sampling procedure, the inherent risk was determined to be %1$s, the control risk was determined to be %2$s and the analytical risk was determined to be %3$s. According to the Audit Risk Model, the required detection risk to maintain an audit risk of %4$s should be %5$s."
msgstr ""
"Model Risiko Audit adalah metode untuk mengurangi informasi yang diperlukan "
"dari sampel pada basis evaluasi sebelumnya dari risiko bawaan, risiko "
"kontrol dan risiko analisis, ketika memelihara risiko audit teringinkan.\n"
"\n"
"Sebelum prosedur pensampelan, risiko bawaan telah ditentukan sebesar %1$s, "
"risiko kontrol telah ditentukan sebesar %2$s dan risiko analisis telah "
"ditentukan sebesar %3$s. Menurut Model Risiko Audit, risiko deteksi yang "
"diperlukan memelihara risiko audit dari %4$s harus berupa %5$s."

msgid "Audit risk (%1$s%%) = Inherent risk (%2$s%%) x Control risk (%3$s%%) x Analytical Risk (%4$s%%) x Detection risk (%5$s%%)"
msgstr ""
"Risiko audit (%1$s%%) = Risiko bawaan (%2$s%%) x Risiko kontrol (%3$s%%) x "
"Risiko analisis (%4$s%%) x Risiko deteksi (%5$s%%)"

