"dalam pemilihan diwarnai dengan merah. Total probabilitas galat tidak "
"melampaui risiko deteksi sebagaimana ditentukan melalui model risiko audit."

msgid "You cannot use an interval-based selection method because the sample size exceeds the population size of %1$s. Please change the selection method to random sampling."
msgstr ""
