msgstr "Distribusi Priori dan Posterior Terharapkan"

msgid "Prior Distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi Priori"

msgid "Prior and Posterior Distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi Priori dan Posterior"

msgid "<b>Figure %1$i.</b> The prior and expected posterior distribution (%2$s) on the population misstatement θ. The prior parameters (%3$s = %4$s, %5$s = %6$s) are derived from the prior information. The expected posterior distribution fulfills the conditions set in the sampling objectives."
msgstr ""
"<b>Figur %1$i.</b> Distribusi priori dan posterior yang diharapkan (%2$s) "
"pada salah saji populasi θ. Parameter priori (%3$s = %4$s, %5$s = %6$s) "
"berasal dari informasi priori. Distribusi posterior yang diharapkan memenuhi "
"rangkaian kondisi dalam objektif pensampelan."

msgid "<b>Figure %1$i.</b> The prior and posterior distribution (%2$s) on the misstatement in the population."
msgstr ""
"<b>Figur %1$i.</b> Distribusi priori dan posterior (%2$s) pada salah saji "
